'''Cheryl''' is a patient who was evacuated during the hospital fire.

==History==
Cheryl was slowly making her way out of the hospital when Jackson found her. She said she just had kidney stones and insisted she could walk, but he saw her struggle to stay upright and carried her out of the hospital.

==Notes and Trivia==
*She objected to being called, "ma'am."
